questionsAndAnswers.question: 1. What types of WordPress websites do you design and develop?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I design and develop a wide range of WordPress websites, including but not limited to e-commerce stores, business websites, portfolios, blogs, educational sites, and personal websites. Whether you need a site for a restaurant, a beauty salon, or a lead generation platform, I can create a custom solu

questionsAndAnswers.question: 2. What is included in your WordPress website design and development service?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
My service includes:

Custom website design and development
Responsive design for all devices
Theme customization (free or premium themes)
User-friendly admin panel
Blog integration
Social media sharing features
Google Maps integration
Custom contact forms
E-commerce functionality (if required)
Basi

questionsAndAnswers.question: 3. Do you offer post-launch support?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I offer ongoing support to ensure your website remains up-to-date and functioning smoothly. This includes troubleshooting issues, making updates, and providing general assistance as needed. I also offer maintenance packages if you require extended support.

questionsAndAnswers.question: 4. Will I be able to manage my website after it’s completed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, absolutely. I provide a user-friendly admin panel and offer guidance on how to manage and update your website. Additionally, I can create tutorial materials or offer training sessions to ensure you feel confident managing your site.

questionsAndAnswers.question: 5. What if I need changes or revisions after the website is completed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I offer unlimited revisions during the development process to ensure the final product meets your expectations. If you require additional changes after the project is completed, I am happy to assist. Depending on the nature of the revisions, there may be additional charges.

Her communication was also spot-on throughout the process, and I felt confident everything would be taken care of. It’s clear that Ayesha puts a lot of effort and care into her work. Keep up the amazing job—your efforts are truly appreciated!

The process was smooth, and her attention to detail was exceptional. My boss is extremely satisfied with the results. I highly recommend Ayesha for any web optimization needs — she is professional, efficient, and truly knows her cr

Wow, Ayesha! The improvements you've made to the website's responsiveness are fantastic. It looks amazing, and I truly appreciate the work you've put into it. Everything is looking great on mobile now. Thank you so much for your excellent work!

She activated the SSL on my website incredibly quickly, making me feel much more secure from potential hackers. The whole process was smooth and efficient, and her professionalism was top-notch. I highly recommend Ayesha to anyone looking for reliable, fast, and quality service. I will definitely be working with her again in the future!
